Task Automation Tracker is a simple Python application that helps
you manage and track your daily tasks using object‑oriented principles.
Each task has attributes like name, priority, duration, and status
flags (started/completed), and methods to start, complete, update priority, and display info.

Features

Create and track multiple tasks

Mark tasks as started and completed, with safeguards

Update task priority at any time

Display a clear summary of each task’s state